  5,106,O ona verit svedok will when jeden z ona umrel robi 2 equitable ludia ona! Ona cestovat potom 2 others robit the svedok! After observing Zmluva Prayer (Salat) let svedok swear GOD alleviate tvoj doubts My nie pouzivat this attain personal zisk vecer testator je related do us! Nor will my zatajit GOD's testimony. Inak my bol sinners
